      <title>随着消费者物价指数 (CPI) 升温导致降息，美元数月来涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/dollar-set-for-best-day-in-three-months-as-cpi-data-sink-bets-on-three-fed-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国通胀数据火爆后，交易员下调了他们预计美联储今年降息的次数，美元创一月以来最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/dollar-set-for-best-day-in-three-months-as-cpi-data-sink-bets-on-three-fed-cuts</guid>
