      <title>交易员在美国消费者物价指数之后削减欧洲央行押注，所有目光都集中在拉加德身上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/traders-pare-ecb-cut-bets-after-us-cpi-with-all-eyes-on-lagarde</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国通胀超过预期后，交易员减少了对欧洲央行降息的押注，市场现在将注意力转向总统克里斯蒂娜·拉加德周四的讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/traders-pare-ecb-cut-bets-after-us-cpi-with-all-eyes-on-lagarde</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 14:06:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
