    <item>
      <title>特朗普前首席财务官艾伦·韦塞尔伯格被判处五个月监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/ex-trump-cfo-weisselberg-is-sentenced-to-five-months-in-jail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)房地产公司的长期首席财务官艾伦·韦塞尔伯格(Allen Weisselberg)因在纽约针对前总统的民事欺诈案中宣誓就职，被判处五个月监禁——魏塞尔伯格第二次入狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/ex-trump-cfo-weisselberg-is-sentenced-to-five-months-in-jail</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 13:41:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀削弱美联储今年降息的理由，收益率飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/yields-soar-as-traders-price-in-just-two-fed-rate-cuts-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于三月份通胀数据高于预期，促使投资者缩减他们预计今年的美国降息幅度，美国国债收益率飙升，创出今年以来的新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/yields-soar-as-traders-price-in-just-two-fed-rate-cuts-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 12:38:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
