      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/cocoa-extends-gain-back-toward-record-high-on-global-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可可在纽约上涨，由于对全球短缺的担忧挥之不去，价格重返历史高位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/cocoa-extends-gain-back-toward-record-high-on-global-shortage</guid>
